WEBVTT

01:40.470 --> 01:45.930
[SPEED AND LOVE]

01:46.229 --> 01:48.830
[Episode 5]

01:52.950 --> 01:53.910
Kak Arak!

01:55.860 --> 01:57.140
Apakah Kak Arak ada?

01:58.420 --> 01:59.259
Kak Arak.

01:59.420 --> 02:00.670
Kak Zhang.

02:00.860 --> 02:01.670
Itu...

02:01.830 --> 02:03.780
Kak Arak pergi ke pusat suku cadang mobil.

02:03.780 --> 02:05.060
Jika kalian punya urusan,

02:05.060 --> 02:05.970
